				www.newegg.com is a good site as others have mentioned. <br>  <br> www.zipzoomfly.com is another good site to buy stuff (formerly googlegear until google the search engine got on their case). <br>  <br> www.pricewatch.com (good general info on prices). <br>  <br> www.hardocp.com (hardware reviews, forums good for getting info). <br>  <br> www.abxzone.com (forums with really nice and helpful people and lots of people testing a variety of setups.  Plus tons of posts on how to build a pc). <br>  <br> www.slickdeals.net (gives some good coupon deals and rebate deals on all kinds of stuff.  You often find dell coupons and offers, as well as hard drives, dvd drives, etc). <br>  <br> www.anandtech.com (hardware reviews, comparisons). <br>  <br> There are many many more but that should get you thoroughly informed.		

