				I built my own machines for years I have piles of them around the house starting with vic 120 and a trs 80. I stoped building my own machines a few years ago. <br> currently I have 2 gaming machines that I bought pre assembled for 200 less than I could bought them for as parts. They have 2.1 amd athlons 1 gig of ram and gforce videos cards. I dont care much for sound so the low in sound blasters work fine. <br> The secret is look for the good deals. I would like to suggest going to best buy and seeing what they have open box. Customers return pc's sometimes and they mark the prices way down. Ofcourse you dont get everything you want but through in a few upgrades; video and ram and you are in bussiness for little money.
